{"tid":1250877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(Now 新聞）發現多個原因令救護延誤","createTime":"2019-06-22T09:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T10:15:04.000Z","uid":36494,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"85aa007157c1fa5d82f174dd995e39580fa0bc75","tid":1250877,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EIDemfSAnmM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEIDemfSAnmM&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh9%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=77c36b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EIDemfSAnmM</a>"},{"pid":"a91ea27c362256daf502ddfae963aec26067e9e6","tid":1250877,"uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:05:01.000Z","msg":"示威者包圍警察總部抗議期間，警方指警總內多人感到不適，召喚救護員到場，近三小時後救護員才能夠將有需要人士送院。我們翻查記錄和片段，發現多個原因令到過程延誤。<br />\n<br />\n示威者包圍警總超過十小時，警方晚上指警總內有人感到不適，需要召喚救護員到場。<br />\n<br />\n根據消防處的資料，晚上9時許接獲緊急求助，指警總內有多人不適。<br />\n<br />\n警方10時許，在社交網站上載圖片，看到兩輛救護車停在分域街近駱克道，並貼文指因為警總出入口被示威者刻意阻塞，召喚救護車超過一小時仍未能抵達警總。<br />\n<br />\n近半小時後，即晚上約11時半，救護車抵達警總夏慤道的側門，救護員推出多張擔架床，步向軍器廠街。<br />\n<br />\n數分鐘後去到警察總部正門外，途中未見示威者阻礙，他們跨過鐵欄在閘外等候，後來轉到另一邊閘門。當時多名立法會議員在場協助，但警總的電閘沒有電力供應，亦鎖上鐵鏈，警員多次來回與救護員溝通，其他警員在後方佈防戒備，擔心示威者趁開閘時衝入。<br />\n<br />\n等候近20分鐘，警方才拉開鐵閘讓救護員入內。相隔約8分鐘，再有另一批救護員帶同擔架床到場，有示威者為他們開路。<br />\n<br />\n結果第一名傷者被抬離警總，此時距離救護員到場已經過了大約50分鐘，部分要送院的人士可以自己步行離開。"},{"pid":"8c5276844684f0a7a1a47b8beb2abe3d5995cdbe","tid":1250877,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:05:27.000Z","msg":"長期 = 聚散<br />\n不求一仗功成，但求齊上齊落"},{"pid":"0e8ba5c4b9e44feab3fa82b0f7695203512816bb","tid":1250877,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"Now高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0527a247389e47d91d1742406012fb5ba7ee113f","tid":1250877,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"now都算唔話得 除咗照直講句警狗扮可憐呃令之外 都算做到盡"},{"pid":"48773269a5ed4468c03a3c921d26e26b9131cb0d","tid":1250877,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0527a247389e47d91d1742406012fb5ba7ee113f","tid":1250877,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"now都算唔話得 除咗照直講句警狗扮可憐呃令之外 都算做到盡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"呃人*"},{"pid":"77a9b84f99d88ba9a17b161ae6c82339e72ad206","tid":1250877,"uid":41610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"浪費服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418af41c9f2040be86de32ae88504bc04332d0b9","tid":1250877,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b630675fdd76a8c1ea933ac661df211bdec4c87","tid":1250877,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"屋企電視壞壞地 淨係睇到now<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfd2d11fd9d29b402ef560ceb08875de2ebcce2","tid":1250877,"uid":56123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"做傳媒唔使話偏幫邊面，只需要講客觀事實已經足夠<br />\n<br />\ncctvb睇得多會壞腦，7點睇viu tv now新聞"},{"pid":"70ee51f9ed224212de841865fe061d7bb65d1350","tid":1250877,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a061e6a916de78c361a1aec0a14b464ed9b6e5d7","tid":1250877,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"推，警察要負責"},{"pid":"bfa14b878ae36f494039c1bd6dbf53d52863f608","tid":1250877,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"9點Call 消防<br />\n10點警察上載FB<br />\n11點架車先到示威區<br />\n<br />\n咁9-11點 救護係邊？"},{